column3: when you think about me do you think about 17 do you think about my old jeep do you think about the stars in the sky
my dad and i split to get a 2014 ford edge
was at the car wash and i was surrounded by corvette audi and bmw. i feel so blessed, but my corolla looked like shit 😩😍😋
😕 i wish my parents would buy me a bmw 😢
